<div><div><h2>Reporter's Take | HR disclosures required before M&A deals</h2></div><div>"moneycontrol newsthe recent exit of flipkart ceo binny bansal after a probe into misconduct complaint brings the spotlight on the non-disclosure of such alleged infractions by employees at the time of a proposed merger or acquisition.the non-disclosure of complaints of material facts or even complaints filed against employees by fellow workers vendors or even contractors could prove fatal prior to an m& a deal.to find out more about the kind of disclosures required before a m& a deal beena parmar is in conversation with m saraswathy. tune in."</div></div>